title: The Clean - Anthology
description:
The Clean's Anthology, organized so you don't have to! You get:

 - the first two singles, Tally Ho and Getting Older, and their b-sides
 - the first two EPs, Boodle Boodle Boodle and Great Sounds Great...
 - selected tracks from the first three LPs, Vehicle, Modern Rock, and Unknown Country
 - some early live tracks
 - some out-takes (one from the second EP, four from the second LP)
 - a very early song, Odditty, collected on the Odditties compilation

The singles and EPs are the classic (subjective), early 80's Clean. A fairly long hiatus stalled the coming of the LPs, released over the course of the 90's. Odditty was covered by Pavement on the "God Save the Clean" tribute album (the track is also now available on Matador's 2008 re-issue of Brighten the Corners, the Nicene Creed Edition).

Enjoy!
